> <br />\n新CEO上場，換緊血，亂緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3033f3f95cbaf321a05fe7e597ec00f49df61d3b","tid":379330,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T05:00:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問吓有無做大車technical野既巴打:<br />\n我想知合德project engineer同technical office既工作有乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依2個post長期請人，請到都雞咁腳走，你抱住我不入地獄誰入地獄嘅心咪試下囉<br />\n<br />\n利申：我估下咋"},{"pid":"aee17e6b9c8b6b3d83dc9a73336edede896d0003","tid":379330,"uid":1074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T11:12:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>諗左好耐想搵一份自己好有興趣既工 <br />\n有冇巴絲打做緊車行,分享下點入行，marketing多唔多請人？ <br />\nsales又有咩要求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPS. 大學畢業差不多3年經驗 讀酒店</blockquote><br />\n做緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點入行？ugrad 之後係jobsdb打公司名search ，send cv<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSales 最緊要識靈活變通，跟得上，大壓力，鐘意車，周圍都請人<br />\n賣到既sales一個月可以搵過十萬，未計自己既二手車買賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  (收車自己錢)<br />\nMkt in house 既都係做coordination ， 因為判晒岀去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 呢行第四年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nHi 巴打<br />\n你做得開唔開心？ <br />\n我對車有興趣，但識既野唔多，易學嗎？ 洗唔洗要識好多車既野先會請？ <br />\n之前掛住返工去玩到上年先去考車，岩岩拎到車牌差不多一年，揸落就覺得幾鍾意，好想買自己第一部全新車。"},{"pid":"8bde193ddf270601e00afef79fbe1b62533e2556","tid":379330,"uid":39781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T16:27:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想問吓有無做大車technical野既巴打:<br />\n我想知合德project engineer同technical office既工作有乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依2個post長期請人，請到都雞咁腳走，你抱住我不入地獄誰入地獄嘅心咪試下囉<br />\n<br />\n利申：我估下咋</blockquote><br />\n講得岩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過現實係無咩人捱到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"686e666b7c703e67bba8778faf6eb74d73ac806f","tid":379330,"uid":39781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T16:41:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>諗左好耐想搵一份自己好有興趣既工 <br />\n有冇巴絲打做緊車行,分享下點入行，marketing多唔多請人？ <br />\nsales又有咩要求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPS. 大學畢業差不多3年經驗 讀酒店</blockquote><br />\n做緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點入行？ugrad 之後係jobsdb打公司名search ，send cv<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSales 最緊要識靈活變通，跟得上，大壓力，鐘意車，周圍都請人<br />\n賣到既sales一個月可以搵過十萬，未計自己既二手車買賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  (收車自己錢)<br />\nMkt in house 既都係做coordination ， 因為判晒岀去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 呢行第四年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nHi 巴打<br />\n你做得開唔開心？ <br />\n我對車有興趣，但識既野唔多，易學嗎？ 洗唔洗要識好多車既野先會請？ <br />\n之前掛住返工去玩到上年先去考車，岩岩拎到車牌差不多一年，揸落就覺得幾鍾意，好想買自己第一部全新車。</blockquote><br />\n如果你當工作係一份工，正正常常無特別<br />\n如果當life time career， 幾開心架，成日對住車，特別係對車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你入大公司(廠)，學既野唔多，全部大路野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但如果你入合德，學到既知識係終生受用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，佢地最驚你唔學，因為車既知識你學唔晒(商用車果套用落私家車)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以捱到既，你會比其他人行得更前更遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講車，商用車果套偏向technical，講既睇既好講技術<br />\n而私家車偏向表面，講外觀內裝馬力，屬impulsive buying  <br />\n<br />\n諗清楚，入左黎呢行好難岀返去<br />\n行頭窄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b45dff5714227d3a7d0de5a5ad4b99fd0e908e1","tid":379330,"uid":39781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T16:44:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>諗左好耐想搵一份自己好有興趣既工 <br />\n有冇巴絲打做緊車行,分享下點入行，marketing多唔多請人？ <br />\nsales又有咩要求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPS. 大學畢業差不多3年經驗 讀酒店</blockquote><br />\n做緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點入行？ugrad 之後係jobsdb打公司名search ，send cv<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSales 最緊要識靈活變通，跟得上，大壓力，鐘意車，周圍都請人<br />\n賣到既sales一個月可以搵過十萬，未計自己既二手車買賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  (收車自己錢)<br />\nMkt in house 既都係做coordination ， 因為判晒岀去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 呢行第四年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nHi 巴打<br />\n你做得開唔開心？ <br />\n我對車有興趣，但識既野唔多，易學嗎？ 洗唔洗要識好多車既野先會請？ <br />\n之前掛住返工去玩到上年先去考車，岩岩拎到車牌差不多一年，揸落就覺得幾鍾意，好想買自己第一部全新車。</blockquote><br />\n如果你當工作係一份工，正正常常無特別<br />\n如果當life time career， 幾開心架，成日對住車，特別係對<span style=\"color: red;\">新</span>車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你入大公司(廠)，<span style=\"color: red;\">容易入，正常人工</span>，學既野唔多，全部大路野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但如果你入合德，學到既知識係終生受用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，佢地最驚你唔學，因為車既知識你學唔晒(商用車果套用落私家車)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以捱到既，你會比其他人行得更前更遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講車，商用車果套偏向technical，講既睇既好講技術<br />\n而私家車偏向表面，講外觀內裝馬力，屬impulsive buying  <br />\n<br />\n諗清楚，<span style=\"color: red;\">無論私家車定貨車</span>入左黎呢行好難岀返去<br />\n行頭窄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"f45cea1d73c26a658e6d38b22e4f18f502c70d89","tid":379330,"uid":122534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T16:44:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問吓有無做大車technical野既巴打:<br />\n我想知合德project engineer同technical office既工作有乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\nProject eng 係賣Product，做tender ， 每一單都係一個project ，唔係速食，預有大量問題<br />\n好處可以接觸唔同既車(巴士，田螺，升降台，消防車)，大公司或政府為主，好多野玩<br />\n壞處？ 捱驢仔，比人屌，一腳踢，問題有機會鑊到仆街，大壓力<br />\n<br />\nTechnical 係對廠，對c fu， 有機會落手落腳做。claim warranty都 claim 到你手軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，而且product 闊，識就OK，唔識就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聽你咁講同出面e&amp;m做既野差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話時話， 知唔知大昌汽車服務中心會唔會好做啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nBBA 好唔好做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nBBA睇你做廠定dealer<br />\n數大壓力大<br />\n當然你賣到就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其中一個品牌，有人三個月賣過百車<br />\n去到請人幫自己打工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n姓杜既?"},{"pid":"1eee3995d63523f72e857626c4c751b7ca3d9069","tid":379330,"uid":39781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T16:52:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問吓有無做大車technical野既巴打:<br />\n我想知合德project engineer同technical office既工作有乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\nProject eng 係賣Product，做tender ， 每一單都係一個project ，唔係速食，預有大量問題<br />\n好處可以接觸唔同既車(巴士，田螺，升降台，消防車)，大公司或政府為主，好多野玩<br />\n壞處？ 捱驢仔，比人屌，一腳踢，問題有機會鑊到仆街，大壓力<br />\n<br />\nTechnical 係對廠，對c fu， 有機會落手落腳做。claim warranty都 claim 到你手軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，而且product 闊，識就OK，唔識就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聽你咁講同出面e&amp;m做既野差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話時話， 知唔知大昌汽車服務中心會唔會好做啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nBBA 好唔好做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" cla