rmal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大細車都做過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點黑暗法？水貨 D km數有幾假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其他唔講<br />\n二手車好處係可以一蚊都唔比簽名拎車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"792b378a8b16623ded0b9fe36f99aecaa449abb8","tid":379330,"uid":1074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T03:33:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>諗左好耐想搵一份自己好有興趣既工 <br />\n有冇巴絲打做緊車行,分享下點入行，marketing多唔多請人？ <br />\nsales又有咩要求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPS. 大學畢業差不多3年經驗 讀酒店</blockquote><br />\n做緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點入行？ugrad 之後係jobsdb打公司名search ，send cv<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSales 最緊要識靈活變通，跟得上，大壓力，鐘意車，周圍都請人<br />\n賣到既sales一個月可以搵過十萬，未計自己既二手車買賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  (收車自己錢)<br />\nMkt in house 既都係做coordination ， 因為判晒岀去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 呢行第四年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nHi 巴打<br />\n你做得開唔開心？ <br />\n我對車有興趣，但識既野唔多，易學嗎？ 洗唔洗要識好多車既野先會請？ <br />\n之前掛住返工去玩到上年先去考車，岩岩拎到車牌差不多一年，揸落就覺得幾鍾意，好想買自己第一部全新車。</blockquote><br />\n如果你當工作係一份工，正正常常無特別<br />\n如果當life time career， 幾開心架，成日對住車，特別係對車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你入大公司(廠)，學既野唔多，全部大路野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但如果你入合德，學到既知識係終生受用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，佢地最驚你唔學，因為車既知識你學唔晒(商用車果套用落私家車)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以捱到既，你會比其他人行得更前更遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講車，商用車果套偏向technical，講既睇既好講技術<br />\n而私家車偏向表面，講外觀內裝馬力，屬impulsive buying  <br />\n<br />\n諗清楚，入左黎呢行好難岀返去<br />\n行頭窄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做sales 搵客難唔難 <br />\n收入賺佣金分成多唔多？ <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d98e6926476ce852cb78ce07c4604443faf3811f","tid":379330,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T03:46:26.000Z","msg":"好做唔做去做騙子"},{"pid":"07144cf56d62557c23798b914407b485f5d10559","tid":379330,"uid":39781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T04:05:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好做唔做去做騙子</blockquote><br />\n買車請去買新車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7542ab5584a92dce3ccde1a1e5c928219936e998","tid":379330,"uid":39781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T04:12:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>諗左好耐想搵一份自己好有興趣既工 <br />\n有冇巴絲打做緊車行,分享下點入行，marketing多唔多請人？ <br />\nsales又有咩要求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPS. 大學畢業差不多3年經驗 讀酒店</blockquote><br />\n做緊<img src=\"/asset